Should work
    % make -f Makefile.quick configure
    % make -f Makefile.quick install

Do the following to get installation help.

    % make -f Makefile.quick

Before doing a 'make -f Makefile.quick all' you can set the CXXFLAGS
as well:

    % setenv CXXFLAGS '-DDEBUG_ManagerActiveStandard'

To recompile only the affected files after making some changes

    % cd build-platform
    % make install
